import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route } from "react-router-dom"
import { Container } from "@mui/material"

import PaginaPublicacao from "../Trabalhos Publicados/PaginaPublicacao"
import {Header, SobreNos, Footer, ImageSlider} from './components/Home/Home';
import Calendar from "../Home/Calendar"

const MainPage = () => {
    return (
        <BrowserRouter>
            <Header />
            <ImageSlider slides={SliderData} />
            <SobreNos />
            <Calendar />
            <Footer />
            <Container sx={{mt:12}}>
                <Routes>
                    <Route path="trabalhoPublico" element={<PaginaPublicacao/>}/>
                    <Route path="listarProfessor" element={<ListarProfessor/>}/>
                    <Route path="editarProfessor" element={<EditarProfessor/>}/>
                </Routes>     
            </Container>
        </BrowserRouter>
    )
}
export default MainPage
